snippet.title: Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl: Gameplay Breakdown
snippet.description:
Thaddeus Crews, Character Designer & Programmer at Ludosity, uses SpongeBob and Patrick to break down the fighting/brawl gameplay of Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl, the fighting game due out this Fall for PlayStation platforms, Xbox platforms, Nintendo Switch, and PC.

#IGN #Gaming
